## Roadmap

- Fix the static reviews_count filter using a dynamic slicer to achieve user-adjustable thresholds instead of a hardcoded 500-review cutoff
- Fix the single relationship between Reviews and Apps using a full star schema with the Categories and Apps_Categories tables to achieve category-level breakdowns of developer responsiveness
- Fix the lack of time-based trend analysis using the lastmod date field to achieve month-over-month tracking of developer responsiveness improvements
- Fix the helpful_reviews calculation using a normalized 0-to-100 scale instead of raw multiplication to achieve easier cross-app comparison


